reviewText: Such a great collection!  Awesome dvds that are fun & informative. Wonderful collection of memorabilia from the blue prints to the id cards & iceberg warnings. A must have for any titanic collector young or old.
Absolutely awesome, highly recommend this for anyone who's interested in the Titanic. The memorabilia is so cool and great to have, they really bring home the tragedy of it all

IN MY 26 YEARS OF ADDING TO MY VARIOUS COLLECTIONS.

 THIS HAS TO BE AND IS, AS FAR AS I'M CONCERNED, ONE OF FINEST COLLECTABLE ITEMS I'VE EVER HAD THE OPPORTUNITY TO TOUCH AND REEXAMINE ALL OF THE MATERIALS INCLUDED IN THIS BOX.

  IT'S AS IF YOU WERE THERE AND A TITANIC PASSENGER AND HAVING "THAT MOMENT" IN HISTORY, WITH YOUR BOARDING PASS IN HAND!!

BUY IT !!! IT'S WELL WORTH THE MONEY.ABSOLUTELY ONE OF THE FINEST COLLECTABLES AROUND!!!
What do you get for the fan who has everything....I know he will love it.
I love this on because I felt I was there and this was the nicest one of all my Titanic books and movies. Love Love Love
